title: Game freezes my computer within a minute or two of match start
body:
So starting about two weeks ago, whenever i try to load into a game, it freezes my computer and i have to force restart it. Queuing up and loading into the game are fine, but as soon as the game begins i have massive lag (despite lowish ping) and fps below 20 (usaully under 10). I tried a lot of things to stop it, including uninstalling and reinstalling multiple times. Today, I reset my computer and i still have the same problems... Any thoughts?
